[orientation=horizontal]:w-full data-[orientation=vertical]:h-full data-[orientation=vertical]:w-px max-w-4xl mx-auto\"></div><section class=\"py-16 md:py-20 bg-muted/30\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"text-center mb-10\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium w-fit whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive transition-[color,box-shadow] overflow-hidden [a&amp;]:hover:bg-accent [a&amp;]:hover:text-accent-foreground mb-4 border-emerald-300 text-emerald-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-3.5 w-3.5 mr-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg>Our Commitment</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4\">Why We Charge</h2><p class=\"text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Small fees keep the platform running and ensure a great experience for everyone.</p></div><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5 flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-server h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"8\" x=\"2\" y=\"2\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><rect width=\"20\" height=\"8\" x=\"2\" y=\"14\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"6\" x2=\"6.01\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">Platform maintenance &amp; server costs</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">Keeping the platform fast, reliable, and available 24/7 across 25+ cities.</p></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5 flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">Fraud prevention &amp; security</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">Advanced fraud detection, content moderation, and account security systems.</p></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5 flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-headphones h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 14h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a9 9 0 0 1 18 0v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-1a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">Customer support team</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">Responsive support team ready to help resolve disputes and answer questions.</p></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5 flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-credit-card h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"5\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"2\" x2=\"22\" y1=\"10\" y2=\"10\"></line></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">Payment processing fees covered by us</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">We absorb Paystack and bank processing fees so you pay less.</p></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-5 flex items-start gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-percent h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><line x1=\"19\" x2=\"5\" y1=\"5\" y2=\"19\"></line><circle cx=\"6.5\" cy=\"6.5\" r=\"2.5\"></circle><circle cx=\"17.5\" cy=\"17.5\" r=\"2.5\"></circle></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">10% service fee on earnings</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1 leading-relaxed\">A 10% platform fee is charged on all earnings (task payouts, product sales, service payments, errand completions). This is automatically deducted before your balance is updated — what you see is what you can withdraw.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"none\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"bg-border shrink-0 data-[orientation=horizontal]:h-px data-[orientation=horizontal]:w-full data-[orientation=vertical]:h-full data-[orientation=vertical]:w-px max-w-4xl mx-auto\"></div><section class=\"py-16 md:py-20\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"text-center mb-10\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium w-fit whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive transition-[color,box-shadow] overflow-hidden [a&amp;]:hover:bg-accent [a&amp;]:hover:text-accent-foreground mb-4 border-emerald-300 text-emerald-700\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-banknote h-3.5 w-3.5 mr-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"12\" x=\"2\" y=\"6\" rx=\"2\"></rect><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle><path d=\"M6 12h.01M18 12h.01\"></path></svg>Payment Options</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4\">Payment Methods</h2><p class=\"text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Multiple payment options to suit your preference.</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 shadow-sm border-2 border-emerald-200\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-credit-card h-6 w-6 text-emerald-700\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"5\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"2\" x2=\"22\" y1=\"10\" y2=\"10\"></line></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Paystack</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Secure card &amp; bank payments</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>Debit &amp; Credit Cards (Visa, Mastercard)</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>Bank Transfer</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>USSD</span></div></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 shadow-sm border-2 border-amber-200\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"h-12 w-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-bitcoin h-6 w-6 text-amber-700\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.767 19.089c4.924.868 6.14-6.025 1.216-6.894m-1.216 6.894L5.86 18.047m5.908 1.042-.347 1.97m1.563-8.864c4.924.869 6.14-6.025 1.215-6.893m-1.215 6.893-3.94-.694m5.155-6.2L8.29 4.26m5.908 1.042.348-1.97M7.48 20.364l3.126-17.727\"></path></svg></div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Paystack Payments</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Secure card &amp; bank transfers</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-amber-600 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>USSD</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-amber-600 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>QR Code</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-amber-600 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>Pay with Bank</span></div></div></div></div></div><p class=\"text-center text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-6\">All payments are processed securely through escrow for buyer and seller protection.</p></div></section><section class=\"py-16 md:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-teal-700 text-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap h-12 w-12 mx-auto mb-6 text-emerald-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6\">Start Posting for Free</h2><p class=\"text-emerald-100 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed\">Join thousands of users who are already posting on PostAll. Most categories are free, and paid listings start as low as ₦500. Get started today!</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center ga